                    <span id="c-454360926" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-454360926" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="454360926">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nuanda/">海喜喜</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-09-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">悲伤往往轻于表达，美好不易言说。清澈的生活，宁静的阿勒泰，所以又干净的文字。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="464407464">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-464407464" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-464407464" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="464407464">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/50393226/">阿辣布猫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-01-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书给我的第一感觉是真实，第二感觉是真挚，再感觉就是真诚了，只有真心实意的去拥抱这个世界，才能让人真切的产生共鸣。我喜欢这本书，它让我心底沉静。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

